80
00:04:15,640 --> 00:04:17,899
Did you really think I would let it slide?

81
00:04:18,720 --> 00:04:19,640
Grandmother.

82
00:04:20,079 --> 00:04:21,640
Didn't you ask me to come here

83
00:04:21,640 --> 00:04:22,520
and say you would arrange

84
00:04:22,520 --> 00:04:23,960
for us to get married?

85
00:04:24,040 --> 00:04:25,920
You're so naive.

86
00:04:27,160 --> 00:04:29,200
I was just using you

87
00:04:29,360 --> 00:04:32,200
to end his thoughts of marrying Qiao Wan.

88
00:04:33,560 --> 00:04:34,800
My grandson's wife

89
00:04:34,800 --> 00:04:36,200
won't be Qiao Wan,

90
00:04:37,159 --> 00:04:39,200
and certainly not you.

91
00:04:40,440 --> 00:04:41,440
Grandmother.

92
00:04:41,720 --> 00:04:43,520
Grandmother.

93
00:04:43,520 --> 00:04:44,720
Mrs. Wang.

94
00:04:46,800 --> 00:04:48,840
Did you understand what the lady said?

95
00:04:48,840 --> 00:04:50,280
You're no longer useful.

96
00:04:50,640 --> 00:04:52,560
Don't come back again.

97
00:04:54,560 --> 00:04:55,360
Grandmother.

98
00:04:55,960 --> 00:04:57,560
