101
00:05:00,640 --> 00:05:01,440
Grandmother.

102
00:05:01,560 --> 00:05:03,200
Grandmother, I was wrong.

103
00:05:09,360 --> 00:05:10,200
Qiao Wan.

104
00:05:10,800 --> 00:05:11,680
Remember this.

105
00:05:12,400 --> 00:05:15,480
Avenging your mother isn't about reclaiming the past.

106
00:05:16,280 --> 00:05:19,010
It's the reason that has kept you going until now.

107
00:05:19,480 --> 00:05:22,000
Those evil people who haven't been punished,

108
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:23,260
especially at the end,

109
00:05:23,720 --> 00:05:25,380
you can't show them any mercy.

110
00:05:34,640 --> 00:05:35,440
Wan Wan.

111
00:05:38,440 --> 00:05:39,440
Why are you here?

112
00:05:40,920 --> 00:05:41,880
You're drunk.

113
00:05:42,440 --> 00:05:43,200
I'm not.

114
00:05:44,560 --> 00:05:45,920
I just wanted to see you.

115
00:05:46,760 --> 00:05:48,640
