118
00:05:59,240 --> 00:06:00,300
Congratulations.

119
00:06:00,600 --> 00:06:02,200
But this is far from enough.

120
00:06:02,480 --> 00:06:04,410
Your retribution is still coming.

121
00:06:06,080 --> 00:06:07,210
Do you believe that?

122
00:06:08,960 --> 00:06:10,320
I just realized

123
00:06:11,480 --> 00:06:13,000
that what I wanted most

124
00:06:14,280 --> 00:06:16,520
was there from the beginning.

125
00:06:18,520 --> 00:06:19,360
Wan Wan.

126
00:06:20,760 --> 00:06:21,600
Come here.

127
00:06:28,320 --> 00:06:30,200
Don't look at me like that.

128
00:06:30,240 --> 00:06:31,800
I'm no worse than Sheng Ze.

129
00:06:31,800 --> 00:06:33,120
The fact that you said it means you've already lost.

130
00:06:33,120 --> 00:06:34,040
Someone like you

131
00:06:34,040 --> 00:06:36,040
doesn't even deserve to be compared to him.

132
00:06:36,040 --> 00:06:36,970
Sheng Huaijing.

133
00:06:37,159 --> 00:06:38,890
I suggest you turn yourself in.

134
00:06:39,360 --> 00:06:40,820
Don't make more mistakes.

135
00:06:41,200 --> 00:06:43,730
This is the last piece of advice I'll give you.

136
00:06:55,480 --> 00:06:57,440
I've been waiting for you for a long time.

137
00:06:57,440 --> 00:06:58,320
Have a seat.

138
00:07:00,640 --> 00:07:02,370
It's just the two of us here now.

139
00:07:02,920 --> 00:07:04,240
You don't need to pretend anymore.

140
00:07:04,240 --> 00:07:05,120
I came here

141
00:07:05,360 --> 00:07:06,960
to get justice for my mother.

142
00:07:08,240 --> 00:07:09,360
You actually

143
00:07:09,840 --> 00:07:12,200
want to expose everything.

144
00:07:12,480 --> 00:07:13,400
Fine.

145
00:07:13,920 --> 00:07:15,280
I'll tell you.

146
00:07:15,560 --> 00:07:16,280
Yes,

147
00:07:17,520 --> 00:07:19,980
I was the one who locked her in that dark room.

148
00:07:26,560 --> 00:07:28,080
Why would you do that?

149
00:07:28,080 --> 00:07:29,240
Why?

150
00:07:30,680 --> 00:07:31,800
Does she dare say

151
00:07:32,120 --> 00:07:34,520
she had nothing to do with the accident?

152
00:07:35,120 --> 00:07:37,840
