158
00:07:46,920 --> 00:07:47,840
do you realize

159
00:07:47,840 --> 00:07:49,500
what crime you've committed?

160
00:07:51,600 --> 00:07:52,560
So what?

161
00:07:53,240 --> 00:07:54,600
It's been so long.

162
00:07:54,600 --> 00:07:56,080
What can you do to me?

163
00:07:58,240 --> 00:08:00,840
You think just because time has passed,

164
00:08:01,520 --> 00:08:03,520
your crimes will disappear?

165
00:08:04,040 --> 00:08:05,880
