168
00:08:12,280 --> 00:08:13,800
Sheng Huaijing?

169
00:08:14,000 --> 00:08:16,120
He'll defend your mother.

170
00:08:16,920 --> 00:08:20,320
After all, when she was locked up,

171
00:08:20,400 --> 00:08:22,800
he never forgot to bring her food.

172
00:08:24,640 --> 00:08:25,680
What did you say?

173
00:08:25,880 --> 00:08:28,340
Sheng Huaijing also visited that dark room.

174
00:08:29,240 --> 00:08:30,360
What are you doing?

175
00:08:31,440 --> 00:08:32,240
Mrs. Wang!

176
00:08:32,520 --> 00:08:33,679
Mrs. Wang.

177
00:08:35,960 --> 00:08:37,440
What am I going to do?

178
00:08:39,760 --> 00:08:41,820
Of course I'm going to lock you up too.

179
00:08:42,520 --> 00:08:44,650
The suffering my mother went through,

180
00:08:45,720 --> 00:08:47,720
you should experience it yourself.

181
00:08:47,920 --> 00:08:49,180
That's fair, isn't it?

182
00:08:51,720 --> 00:08:53,240
I didn't drive her insane.

183
00:08:54,560 --> 00:08:56,880
I only locked her up for a while.

184
00:08:57,680 --> 00:08:59,240
When she was released,

185
00:08:59,720 --> 00:09:01,640
