186
00:09:02,320 --> 00:09:03,640
It's not my fault.

187
00:09:04,560 --> 00:09:05,880
You can't lock me up.

188
00:09:06,120 --> 00:09:08,160
You can't lock me up.

189
00:09:11,160 --> 00:09:12,200
It's me.

190
00:09:13,920 --> 00:09:15,160
It's my fault.

191
00:09:15,800 --> 00:09:18,280
It's all my fault, this old woman's mistake.

192
00:09:20,240 --> 00:09:21,720
Back then, I

193
00:09:22,200 --> 00:09:24,840
was blinded by anger.

194
00:09:25,760 --> 00:09:28,760
I just wanted to teach her a lesson.

195
00:09:29,600 --> 00:09:30,460
I never thought

196
00:09:32,200 --> 00:09:34,960
